{"tid":581870,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無諗過，點解人要生存？","createTime":"2018-03-05T16:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T05:35:15.000Z","uid":27114,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"66b2254938f1a69c94e3605abc78b277e2416819","tid":581870,"uid":27114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T16:41:50.000Z","msg":"好多人都講過，香港人好涯得，但係點解生活要涯？<br />\n有人話，用20幾年時間讀書 40幾年時間工作，就係為咗退休享受生活，但係到左咗60幾歲仲真係可以享受生活咩？我就覺得換黎嘅係周第身骨痛無所事事咁係到等完結。<br />\n講真，我好羨慕可以周圍旅行嘅人，佢地嘅生活一定係開心多過辛苦。<br />\n究竟人生意義係啲咩，每一日早起身返工返學，做到狗咁聽日繼續咁嘅生活，究竟目標係乜嘢？<br />\n呢一刻，我覺得好迷惘生活係呢個世上 純粹發洩"},{"pid":"7697c666be2b8aca13116f69e388387c04f19b9e","tid":581870,"uid":134099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T16:44:27.000Z","msg":"雖然迷惘都真係好無方向感 但都總算係尋找嘅過程呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總好過求求其其揀啲唔啱嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541c6e6220d10d5b0859c9f103db57b1bddba7fe","tid":581870,"uid":125976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T16:45:59.000Z","msg":"因為你唔生存，你上面班貴族點可以繼續享受呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6dc2b3747b42926bffb92ea274df19c47fae1d9","tid":581870,"uid":134099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"541c6e6220d10d5b0859c9f103db57b1bddba7fe","tid":581870,"uid":125976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T16:45:59.000Z","msg":"因為你唔生存，你上面班貴族點可以繼續享受呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T16:47:52.000Z","msg":"呢個世界總需要你呢啲咁嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aade2c96e437f8c8e8dd3155cec27d10c95f438","tid":581870,"uid":77614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T16:48:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e471f365fef8c0fff23bf6e1936c49d59c120621","tid":581870,"uid":27114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7697c666be2b8aca13116f69e388